title: Stormring Temple
story: For decades the temple was considered lost. Currently it is overrun with chickens. Word is that countless treasures of gold and jewels and ancient books are stored here.

notes.text: A corpse of an elf, some gold nearby.
A comb of invocation on a pedestal.
A graffiti depicting the land around the temple.
A large double door with two keyholes on the western wall.
A key among rubble on the ground.
